&lt;h2 id=&#34;automated-deployment&#34;&gt;Automated Deployment
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;rainyun-virtual-host-discontinued&#34;&gt;Rainyun Virtual Host (Discontinued)
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;If using Rainyun Virtual Host (discontinued), manually add the certificate first:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Go to &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://app.rainyun.com/apps/ssl/list/free-ssl&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34; &gt;SSL Certificate Center&lt;/a&gt;

&lt;span style=&#34;white-space: nowrap;&#34;&gt;&lt;svg width=&#34;.7em&#34; height=&#34;.7em&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 21 21&#34;
        xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34;&gt;
        &lt;path d=&#34;m13 3l3.293 3.293l-7 7l1.414 1.414l7-7L21 11V3z&#34; fill=&#34;currentColor&#34; /&gt;
        &lt;path d=&#34;M19 19H5V5h7l-2-2H5c-1.103 0-2 .897-2 2v14c0 1.103.897 2 2 2h14c1.103 0 2-.897 2-2v-5l-2-2v7z&#34;
            fill=&#34;currentColor&#34;&gt;
    &lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
.&lt;br&gt;
&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/post/2025050101/QQ_1746085892100.png&#34;
	width=&#34;374&#34;
	height=&#34;57&#34;
	srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/post/2025050101/QQ_1746085892100_hu_eda7b8f99671d86.png 480w, http://localhost:1313/post/2025050101/QQ_1746085892100_hu_55257259186929fb.png 1024w&#34;
